astraiea.layer2.generators.artefacts

Class MultipleArtefactOutput<T extends GeneratorOutput>

  • java.lang.Object
    • astraiea.layer2.generators.GeneratorOutput
      • astraiea.layer2.generators.artefacts.MultipleArtefactOutput<T>

  • public class MultipleArtefactOutput<T extends GeneratorOutput>
extends GeneratorOutput
    FIXME Refactoring 27/11 - new class. Encapsulates the output produced by running multiple repeats on one artefact in problems which involve multiple artefacts. Ensures compliance with Hitchhikers advice for multiple artefact problems such as taking the average of these runs and performing a large number of repeats.
    Author:
    Geoffrey Neumann
